{"tid":1361853,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人必須卸下的包袱","createTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T17:26:30.000Z","uid":167355,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4383df33bd66e6e406b5f5c5a02c7bd2f6ae868d","tid":1361853,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"香港人，有好多包袱<br />\n最無包袱既年輕人（啫係我地十幾廿歲既人）<br />\n今日連登好多post都係各個政府部門既職員<br />\n表示自己既立場，真心好多謝你<br />\n但唔好意思，我知我有啲強差人意，<br />\n但係無你地既<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">堂堂正正既罷工</span></strong></span><br />\n係唔會撼動到政府。<br />\n如果可以 覺得有得做 大家商量個日子 <br />\n相信好多人都會去同行 你絕不孤單<br />\n<br />\n今日係69至今既第45日<br />\n我希望大家堅持下去<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>就算失望 不能絕望</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9b4822017b98c31e390ccfe43a9cb01b2e928146","tid":1361853,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"68f8b19946af913f0f4fae3b27cf3328127d7640","tid":1361853,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:49:50.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"ce4d49420e0e54052ac663949e83d1231330a7a8","tid":1361853,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>更正版文宣</strong></span></span><br />\n盡貼大家共識 呢張最主要係想叫到多啲人參加<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67aycf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F67aycf2.jpg&h=98790fe1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2676f540dd7b1eec60bdd6660a29fd8481d5bb25","tid":1361853,"uid":201374,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"其實係<br />\n但叫香港人罷工，難過叫共產黨落台"},{"pid":"29528dcc113135865fb647671a6482627ec3b325","tid":1361853,"uid":167355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"罷工看似遙不可及 但意義重大"},{"pid":"1607b0927b0